This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) because it describes a system for building and managing a multilingual terminology dictionary. It may also belong to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) because the system involves organizing and searching through large amounts of data. Additionally, the use of machine learning and natural language processing techniques suggests that it could fall under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Deep Learning (cs.DL).
